        <abstract>
            <p>JS does not fully accept natural selection.</p>
            <p>Has never raised oxlips from cowslips or primroses; reports of such must be cases of crossing.</p>
            <p>Discusses relative fertility of varieties, self-fertility of hybrids, and plans for experiments on enhanced hybrid fertility.</p>
        </abstract>
